name: Christmas Cow
description:
This artwork was made by 11 year old IWannaBeACow.  

She used two different online photos as reference photos, painted each herself on two different canvases and then with help from mentor used Photoshop to combine the two paintings into one, then added some of her previous artworks to the ornaments.

Artist does not have a Twitter, please contact art mentor, Lily White @rblbab with any questions or comments, thank you!
